{"tid":1512584,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"緊急法.... 係叫隱形有錢阿婆去銀行攞錢契機!!!","createTime":"2019-08-28T02:56:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T02:57:59.000Z","uid":277060,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"3fb02c3d349ff2dd0a1f18b35b23e719e8de8444","tid":1512584,"uid":277060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T02:56:03.000Z","msg":"緊急法裡面有一條條文寫住:<br />\n(f) 對財產及其使用作出的撥配、管制、沒收及處置；<br />\n即係話其實可以凍結銀行資產等等。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所以，我地要整定長輩圖，如果建制再吹搞緊急法，或者出老解、戒嚴諸如此類。就大力文宣猛攻，叫 D 阿婆去銀行拎晒 D 錢出黎。如果而家唔拎遲 D 就無得拎。</span></span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n我同你講，香港其實好多阿婆有錢到你唔信，佢一個肯將銀行 D 錢拎出黎隨時好過我地十個兄弟做同樣O既野。最緊要O既係，佢地做其他長者先會信香港銀行唔夠錢，一傳十十傳百，銀行先會擠提。"},{"pid":"6271ac6ac91cb9924fd8304d449720f1721464a3","tid":1512584,"uid":284522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T02:56:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQyWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=e1435487\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQyWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=8843012b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQyWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=7f43ecee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"952da63709660f86988ce7d4a44da676ebbdca6e","tid":1512584,"uid":89145,"l